---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
	title="Deanery of Windsor-Essex"
	description="Welcome to the Deanery of Windsor-Essex, a community of Catholic parishes serving the faithful in Windsor-Essex County, Ontario."
>
	<!-- Hero/Jumbotron Section -->
	<section class="bg-linear-to-br from-blue-600 to-blue-800 text-white">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 sm:py-28 lg:py-36">
			<div class="text-center">
				<h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6">
					Deanery of Windsor-Essex
				</h1>
				<p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-blue-100 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
					A community of Catholic parishes serving the faithful in Windsor-Essex County, Ontario
				</p>
				<a
					href="/mass-finder"
					class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 text-lg font-semibold rounded-lg bg-white text-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl"
				>
					Find Mass, Confession, & Adoration Times
					<svg class="ml-2 w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
					</svg>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- About Section -->
	<section class="py-16 sm:py-20 bg-white">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-8">
				About the Deanery
			</h2>
			<div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-600 space-y-6">
				<p>
					The Deanery of Windsor-Essex is a vibrant collection of Catholic parishes united in faith and service 
					within the Diocese of London. Our deanery encompasses the beautiful Windsor-Essex County region, 
					serving thousands of faithful Catholics through our many parishes and worship communities.
				</p>
				<p>
					Each parish in our deanery offers a unique spiritual home while sharing in the universal mission 
					of the Catholic Church: to proclaim the Gospel, celebrate the sacraments, and serve those in need. 
					From the urban parishes of Windsor to the rural communities throughout Essex County, we are united 
					in our commitment to worship, fellowship, and Christian service.
				</p>
				<p>
					Whether you're a lifelong parishioner, new to the area, or simply visiting, we warmly welcome you 
					to explore our parishes and join us in celebrating the Holy Mass. Use our schedule finder to 
					discover Mass, confession, and adoration times at churches near you.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Quick Links Section -->
	<section class="py-16 sm:py-20 bg-gray-50">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-12">
				Explore Our Resources
			</h2>
			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
				<a 
					href="/mass-finder" 
					class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow p-6 group"
				>
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-blue-200 transition-colors">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Mass, Confession, & Adoration Times</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-600">
						Find schedules for Mass, confession, and adoration at parishes throughout Windsor-Essex.
					</p>
				</a>
				<a 
					href="/parishes" 
					class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow p-6 group"
				>
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-green-200 transition-colors">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" />
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Our Parishes</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-600">
						Explore our Families of Parishes and discover the churches that make up our deanery.
					</p>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>